# Reckoning House — Illustration Prompt

Create a richly detailed, roughly square digital painting sized to sit beside narrative text on desktop or mobile screens. Depict a grounded late-medieval harbor campaign setting with historically plausible merchant-finance interiors, wax seals, tally sticks, ledgers, benches, and narrow harbor windows. Emphasize crisp readability, brighter maritime color accents, and clear spatial separation more than muddy painterly atmosphere.

- Composition: tense interior of a harbor counting room with an open path back toward Harbor Road and another exit toward the salt storehouses.
- Key elements: angry venture lords, open ledgers, sanded ink, wax seals, and a prominently reachable venture seal on the table.
- Character focus: furious financiers who insist the ship is entirely ready while blaming everybody else.
- Navigation hint: keep both the uphill town return and the downhill working-harbor exit visually obvious.

